# Marketplace-Loyalty UI/UX Rules

## Stack

- Vite + React + TypeScript (strict). UI built **exclusively** with shadcn/ui components on Tailwind CSS.
- Add shadcn components via the CLI (`npx shadcn@latest add <component>`) into `src/components/ui/`. Never hand-write a replacement for a component shadcn already provides (button, dialog, table, form, select, toast, etc.).
- `src/components/ui/` is generated code: restyle via tokens/variants, do not fork component logic. App-specific composites live in `src/components/shared/`.
- Icons: `lucide-react` only. Charts: shadcn Chart components (Recharts).
- Never hardcode colors in components (`bg-[#002379]` is forbidden). Use semantic Tailwind classes backed by the CSS variables below (`bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`, …).

## Color palette

Brand primary is **#002379** (deep navy, hsl(223 100% 24%)) — anchored as step 800 of the primary scale.

### Primary — "Marketplace Navy"

| Step | Hex | Usage |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 50 | `#E8EDFF` | Tinted backgrounds, selected rows |
| 100 | `#D4DEFF` | Hover tints, badges background |
| 200 | `#A9BDFF` | Borders on tinted surfaces |
| 300 | `#7E9BFF` | Decorative, charts |
| 400 | `#5379FF` | Links on dark surfaces, charts |
| 500 | `#2857F0` | Interactive accents, focus glow |
| 600 | `#1240C4` | Link text, hover state of primary buttons |
| 700 | `#06309C` | Active/pressed state of primary buttons |
| **800** | **`#002379`** | **Brand primary — buttons, sidebar, key actions** |
| 900 | `#001A59` | Dark surfaces, portal hero background |
| 950 | `#001038` | Darkest surface, dark-mode background |

### Accent — "Reward Gold" (complementary to navy; reserved for loyalty moments)

| Step | Hex | Usage |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 100 | `#FFF3D6` | Gold tinted backgrounds |
| 400 | `#FFC233` | Points icons, tier highlights |
| 500 | `#FFB200` | Points values, celebration moments, "Redeem" emphasis |
| 600 | `#D99700` | Gold text on light backgrounds (meets contrast) |

Gold is an *earned-value* signal: points balances, rewards, tier badges, celebrations. Do not use it for generic CTAs or decoration — navy stays the workhorse.

### Semantic

| Role | Hex | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Success | `#16A34A` | Points earned, fulfilled, active |
| Warning | `#F59E0B` | Expiring points, low inventory |
| Destructive | `#DC2626` | Revoke, delete, failed deliveries |
| Info | `#0284C7` | Neutral notices |

### Neutrals

Use Tailwind **slate** (cool gray, harmonizes with navy). Body text `slate-900` on white; secondary text `slate-500`; borders `slate-200`; page background `slate-50` (admin) / white (portal).

### shadcn CSS variables (`src/styles/globals.css`)

```css
:root {
  --background: 0 0% 100%;
  --foreground: 222 47% 11%;
  --card: 0 0% 100%;
  --card-foreground: 222 47% 11%;
  --popover: 0 0% 100%;
  --popover-foreground: 222 47% 11%;
  --primary: 223 100% 24%;            /* #002379 */
  --primary-foreground: 0 0% 100%;
  --secondary: 223 100% 95%;          /* primary-50 */
  --secondary-foreground: 223 100% 24%;
  --muted: 210 40% 96%;
  --muted-foreground: 215 16% 47%;
  --accent: 223 100% 95%;             /* subtle hover surface */
  --accent-foreground: 223 100% 24%;
  --destructive: 0 72% 51%;
  --destructive-foreground: 0 0% 100%;
  --border: 214 32% 91%;
  --input: 214 32% 91%;
  --ring: 223 100% 24%;
  --radius: 0.5rem;
  /* brand extras */
  --gold: 42 100% 50%;                /* #FFB200 */
  --gold-foreground: 36 100% 15%;
  --success: 142 72% 36%;
  --warning: 38 92% 50%;
